1.a

Khẳng định nào sau đây là SAI :

 

2.A

\[\lim \frac{{1 + \frac{1}{{{n^2}}} + \frac{1}{{{n^3}}}}}{{2 + \frac{1}{n} + \frac{2}{{{n^3}}}}} = \frac{1}{2}\]

 

2.B

\[\lim \frac{{{{\left( {\frac{1}{4}} \right)}^n} - 1 + {{\left( {\frac{3}{4}} \right)}^n}}}{{2 + {{\left( {\frac{1}{2}} \right)}^n}}} = \frac{{ - 1}}{2}\]

 

2.C

\[\lim \frac{{{{\left( {\frac{1}{2}} \right)}^n} - 3 + {{\left( {\frac{1}{4}} \right)}^n}}}{{4 - {{\left( {\frac{1}{3}} \right)}^n}}} = \frac{3}{4}\]

 

2.D

\[\lim \frac{{3 + \frac{1}{n} + \frac{1}{{{n^2}}}}}{{\sqrt {4 - \frac{1}{n} + \frac{1}{{{n^2}}}} }} = \frac{3}{2}\]

 

3.

Đáp án

C

 

4.Đáp án

chi tiết

\[\lim \frac{{1 + \frac{1}{{{n^2}}} + \frac{1}{{{n^3}}}}}{{2 + \frac{1}{n} + \frac{2}{{{n^3}}}}} = \frac{{1 + 0 + 0}}{{2 + 0 + 0}} = \frac{1}{2}\]

 ;

\[\lim \frac{{{{\left( {\frac{1}{4}} \right)}^n} - 1 + {{\left( {\frac{3}{4}} \right)}^n}}}{{2 + {{\left( {\frac{1}{2}} \right)}^n}}} = \frac{{0 - 1 + 0}}{{2 + 0}} = \frac{{ - 1}}{2}\]

\[\lim \frac{{{{\left( {\frac{1}{2}} \right)}^n} - 3 + {{\left( {\frac{1}{4}} \right)}^n}}}{{4 - {{\left( {\frac{1}{3}} \right)}^n}}} = \frac{{0 - 3 + 0}}{{4 - 0}} = \frac{{ - 3}}{4}\]

 ;

\[\lim \frac{{3 + \frac{1}{n} + \frac{1}{{{n^2}}}}}{{\sqrt {4 - \frac{1}{n} + \frac{1}{{{n^2}}}} }} = \frac{{3 + 0 + 0}}{{\sqrt {4 - 0 + 0} }} = \frac{3}{2}\]

6.Ghi chú

 

 

1.b

Kh

ẳng định sau khẳng định nào SAI:

 

2.A

\[\lim \frac{{5{n^4} - {n^3} + n + 1}}{{2{n^2} + n + 7}} = + \infty \]

 

2.B

\[\lim \frac{{{n^3} + 2n - 1}}{{n + 1}} = + \infty \]

 

2.C

\[\lim \frac{{{{\left( {{n^2} - 1} \right)}^3}.{{\left( {3{n^3} + 1} \right)}^2}}}{{{{\left( {4{n^3} + 2n - 1} \right)}^4}}} = \frac{9}{{256}}\]

 

2.D

\[\lim \frac{{3n - 11}}{{{n^4} + 3{n^3} - n + 2}} = + \infty \]

 

3.Đáp án

D

 

4.Đáp án chi tiết

\[\lim \frac{{5{n^4} - {n^3} + n + 1}}{{2{n^2} + n + 7}} = \lim \frac{{5 - \frac{1}{n} + \frac{1}{{{n^3}}} + \frac{1}{{{n^4}}}}}{{\frac{2}{{{n^2}}} + \frac{1}{{{n^3}}} + \frac{7}{{{n^4}}}}} = + \infty \]

;

\[\lim \frac{{{n^3} + 2n - 1}}{{n + 1}} = \lim \frac{{1 + \frac{2}{{{n^2}}} - \frac{1}{{{n^3}}}}}{{\frac{1}{{{n^2}}} + \frac{1}{{{n^3}}}}} = \frac{1}{0} = + \infty \]

;

\[\lim \frac{{{{\left( {{n^2} - 1} \right)}^3}.{{\left( {3{n^3} + 1} \right)}^2}}}{{{{\left( {4{n^3} + 2n - 1} \right)}^4}}} = \lim \frac{{{{\left( {1 - \frac{1}{{{n^2}}}} \right)}^3}.{{\left( {3 + \frac{1}{{{n^3}}}} \right)}^2}}}{{{{\left( {4 + \frac{2}{{{n^2}}} - \frac{1}{{{n^3}}}} \right)}^4}}} = \frac{9}{{256}}\]

 ;

\[\lim

\frac{{3n - 11}}{{{n^4} + 3{n^3} - n + 2}} = \lim \frac{{\frac{3}{{{n^3}}} - \frac{{11}}{{{n^4}}}}}{{1 + \frac{3}{n} - \frac{1}{{{n^3}}} + \frac{2}{{{n^4}}}}} = 0\]
